1. *Pesmu* je napisao njegov dobar prijatelj. (He wrote the song his good friend.)
2. On je pevao *pesmu* deci. (He sang the song to the children.)
3. Ona uči da sama sastavi *pesmu*. (She is learning to compose a song by herself.)
4. *Pesmu* je pevala na svom prvom nastupu. (She sang the song at her first performance.)
5. On će naučiti *pesmu* za naredni događaj. (He will learn the song for the next event.)
6. Ona je napisala svoju prvu *pesmu*. (She wrote her first song.)